<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account and Two-Factor Authentication Verified</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #3e3e3e;
        }

        .email-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 600px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            padding: 10px;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }

        .success-message {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .two-factor-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: #3e3e3e;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Account and Two-Factor Authentication Verified!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>Your account has been successfully verified. Additionally, Two-Factor Authentication (2FA) has been
                enabled for added security.</p>
            <p>We are thrilled to have you on board and ensure your account is safe. If you have any questions or need
                assistance, feel free to contact
                our support team.</p>
            <div class="success-message">
                Thank you for verifying your account and enabling 2FA!
            </div>
            <div class="two-factor-info">
                <p><strong>Important:</strong> With 2FA enabled, you'll receive a code to your email for login
                    verification. Make sure to keep your email secure.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>